summary: what would brie larson do if she found out you werent wearing panties under your dress at a movie premiere?
question: what would brie larson do if she found out you werent wearing panties under your dress at a movie premiere?
answer: The thing about those big premiers is is that there are people everywhere. She couldn’t disappear with you for a few minutes and get her face under that dress. So she’d be on edge the whole night, skipping the afterparty and taking you straight to your hotel room to have her way with you.

title: Hey Tumblr,
body:
I’m just saying, tumblr asked for RDJ to have a baby girl…and he had a baby girl. Tumblr asked for Brie Larson to be Captain Marvel…. and now she’s Captain Marvel.

So.. since Tumblr is obviously full of witches..

How about we work on getting Chris Evans in a live action Disney Hercules movie? Think about how great it would be. You know you want it, let’s make it happen!

summary:
“The first time I got a spread in a fashion magazine there was a 
one-off piece of clothing from the runway. I asked, “Can you...
caption: “The first time I got a spread in a fashion magazine there was a one-off piece of clothing from the runway. I asked, “Can you only be in magazines if you’re the size of this one piece?” There was this silence. Men get custom suits or shirts made to fit, but as women, if you don’t fit into that sample you bump up against an aspect of your career you can never blossom into.”
